"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/daughter-of-the-dragon-review-the-movie-star-from-chinatown-90311c2f?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《龙的女儿》评论：来自唐人街的明星</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/daughter-of-the-dragon-review-the-movie-star-from-chinatown-90311c2f"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-833247?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">埃弗里特收藏</span></div></div></div><p>黄柳霜的迷人风采使她在电影默片时代成为全球名人。但好莱坞的偏见让主角望而却步。<em>朱莉娅·弗林·西勒的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/daughter-of-the-dragon-review-the-movie-star-from-chinatown-90311c2f?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
